📘 I/O and NIO.2 – OCP Summary
Concept	                Classic IO (java.io)	            NIO.2 (java.nio.file)
File handling	        FileReader, BufferedWriter, etc.	Path, Files, DirectoryStream
Performance	Blocking	Better                              scalability + non-blocking I/O
New file APIs	        ✖️	                                ✔️ Files.copy, Files.move, Files.walk
Watching FS changes	    ✖️	                                ✔️ WatchService
Walking file trees	    Manual recursion	                ✔️ FileVisitor & Files.walkFileTree()